sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Gateway as Istio Ingress Gateway<br/>istio-system<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Passthrough
    participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>{isvc-namespace}<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
    participant Container as Model Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP localhost

    Note over Client,Container: Flow 1: External Model Inference Request (KServe Mode)

    Client->>Router: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)<br/>TLS 1.2+
    Router->>Gateway: Forward (TLS passthrough)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Gateway->>Predictor: Inference Request<br/>mTLS (Istio sidecar)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Predictor->>Container: Localhost request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Container-->>Predictor: Prediction Result
    Predictor-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,Container: Flow 2: Prometheus Metrics Scraping

    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>{monitoring-namespace}
    participant CtrlMetrics as Controller Metrics Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PredMetrics1 as Predictor Metrics (Caikit)<br/>8086/TCP HTTP
    participant PredMetrics2 as Predictor Metrics (TGIS)<br/>3000/TCP HTTP

    Prom->>CtrlMetrics: GET /metrics<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    CtrlMetrics-->>Prom: Controller Metrics
    Prom->>PredMetrics1: GET /metrics<br/>ServiceAccount Token<br/>NetworkPolicy allowed
    PredMetrics1-->>Prom: Caikit Metrics
    Prom->>PredMetrics2: GET /metrics<br/>ServiceAccount Token<br/>NetworkPolicy allowed
    PredMetrics2-->>Prom: TGIS Metrics

    Note over Client,Container: Flow 3: Controller Reconciliation

    participant Ctrl as Controller Pod
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant IstioAPI as Istio API<br/>15017/TCP HTTPS mTLS

    Ctrl->>K8s: Watch InferenceService CRs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>Ctrl: ISVC events
    Ctrl->>K8s: Create/Update Resources<br/>(Routes, NetworkPolicies, etc)
    K8s-->>Ctrl: Confirmation
    Ctrl->>IstioAPI: Create VirtualService, PeerAuth<br/>ServiceAccount Token (mTLS)
    IstioAPI-->>Ctrl: Confirmation

    Note over Client,Container: Flow 4: ModelMesh Inference Request

    participant MMClient as Internal Client
    participant MMSvc as ModelMesh Service<br/>8008/TCP HTTP or<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    MMClient->>MMSvc: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>8008/TCP HTTP (plaintext)<br/>or 8443/TCP HTTPS (mTLS optional)
    MMSvc-->>MMClient: Inference Response
